ines</a> – 💬 <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/minecraft\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Community Support</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/Minecraft-Support\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Mojang Support (Technical Issues)</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://support.xbox.com/contact-us/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Microsoft Support (Account Issues)</a> – 📓 <a href=\"https://report.bugs.mojang.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/2\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Project Summary</a> – ✍️ <a href=\"https://aka.ms/MinecraftFeedbackDiscord\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Feedback and Suggestions</a> – 📖 <a href=\"https://minecraft.wiki/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Game Wiki</a></p>",
